FBIS4-38248 "drnes125_j_94012" FBIS-NES-94-125 Daily Report 28 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Salih Tells al-Qadhdhafi North Accepts Cease-Fire Salih Tells al-Qadhdhafi North Accepts Cease-Fire LD2806123294 Tripoli Voice of Greater Arab Homeland in Arabic 1100 GMT 28 Jun 94 LD2806123294 Tripoli Voice of Greater Arab Homeland Arabic BFN [Text] The brother leader of the revolution [Colonel Mu'ammar al-Qadhdhafi] has received a telephone call from Yemeni President 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, in which the latter explained to him the situation in Yemen and informed him of his acceptance of the cease-fire and negotiations with the Yemeni Socialist Party [YSP].
